<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>자살예방법 제4조, 국가의 책무 — 세계일보 탐사보도팀</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Noto+Serif+KR:wght@300;400;600&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --black: #0e0e0e;
    --off-white: #ffffff;
    --accent: #009e2f;
    --text: #1a1a1a;
    --muted: #6b6560;
    --border: rgba(0,158,47,0.25);
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    background: var(--off-white);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.24em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--accent), transparent);
    margin: 0 2.8rem;
    opacity: 0.35;
  }

  /* ─── 배너 ─── */
  .crisis-bar {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 200;
    background: rgba(10,10,10,0.93);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,158,47,0.4);
    padding: 0.8rem 2.8rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
    transform: translateY(100%);
    transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1);
  }
  .crisis-bar.visible { transform: translateY(0); }
  .crisis-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0; width: 22px; height: 22px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--accent); border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .crisis-icon::after { content:'※'; font-size:0.6rem; color:var(--accent); }
  .crisis-text {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    font-size: 0.88rem; line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-weight: 300; flex: 1;
  }
  .crisis-text strong { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }
  .crisis-close {
    flex-shrink: 0; background: none; border: none;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); font-size: 1rem; cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem; transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .crisis-close:hover { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }

  /* ─── HERO ─── */
  .hero {
    position: relative; height: 100vh; min-height: 600px;
    display: flex; align-items: flex-end; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: url('hero.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
    filter: brightness(0.5); transform: scale(1.04);
    animation: heroZoom 14s ease-out forwards;
  }
  @keyframes heroZoom { from{transform:scale(1.04);} to{transform:scale(1.0);} }
  .hero-content {
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    padding: 0 2.8rem 5rem; max-width: 900px;
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px);
    animation: fadeUp 1s 0.5s ease forwards;
  }
  @keyframes fadeUp { to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);} }
  @keyframes fadeIn { to{opacity:1;} }
  .hero-label {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1rem,2.2vw,1.5rem); font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82); margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem,5vw,4.5rem); font-weight: 450;
    color: #fff; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem,1.8vw,1.2rem);
    color: var(--accent); font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }
  .scroll-indicator {
    position: absolute; bottom: 2.2rem; right: 2.8rem;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeIn 1s 1.4s forwards;
  }
  .scroll-indicator span {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.58rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); writing-mode: vertical-rl;
  }
  .scroll-line {
    width: 1px; height: 52px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom,rgba(255,255,255,0.45),transparent);
    animation: scrollPulse 2.2s infinite;
  }
  @keyframes scrollPulse { 0%,100%{opacity:0.35;} 50%{opacity:1;} }

  .reveal {
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px);
    transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }

  /* ─── 그래프 ─── */
  .chart-section {
    padding: 6rem 2.8rem;
    max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .chart-intro {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem,2vw,1.4rem); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 3rem; max-width: 680px;
  }
  .chart-intro strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }
  .chart-wrap { width: 100%; overflow-x: auto; position: relative; }
  svg.line-chart { display: block; width: 100%; }
  .chart-source {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); margin-top: 1rem; text-align: right;
  }

  /* 툴팁 */
  .chart-tooltip {
    position: absolute;
    background: var(--black);
    color: #fff;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    padding: 0.4rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.15s;
    white-space: nowrap;
    transform: translate(-50%, -130%);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
  }
  .chart-tooltip.show { opacity: 1; }

  /* ─── 숫자 카드 ─── */
  .numbers-section {
    padding: 6rem 2.8rem;
    max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .numbers-section > .section-label { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .numbers-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr);
    gap: 1px; background: var(--border);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .number-card {
    background: var(--off-white);
    padding: 2.8rem 2.2rem;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.8rem;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .number-card::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0;
    height: 3px; width: 0;
    background: var(--accent);
    transition: width 1.2s ease;
  }
  .number-card.counted::after { width: 100%; }

  .number-big {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: clamp(2rem,4vw,3.2rem);
    font-weight: 500; color: var(--accent); line-height: 1;
    min-height: 1.2em;
  }
  .number-unit {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-top: 0.1rem;
  }
  .number-desc {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--muted); font-weight: 300;
  }
  .number-desc strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }

  /* ─── LEAD ─── */
  .lead-section {
    padding: 7rem 2.8rem 6rem;
    max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .lead-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem,2.8vw,2rem); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--black);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); padding-left: 1.4rem;
  }
  .lead-text { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 2.1; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 300; }
  .lead-text p + p { margin-top: 1.2rem; }

  /* ─── 티저 ─── */
  .teaser-section { padding: 2rem 0 4rem; }
  .teaser-item {
    position: relative; height: 100vh; min-height: 560px;
    display: flex; align-items: flex-end; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .teaser-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-size: cover; background-position: center;
    filter: brightness(0.4);
    transition: transform 0.7s ease;
  }
  .teaser-item:hover .teaser-bg { transform: scale(1.02); }
  .teaser-bg-1 { background-image: url('./images/thumb1.jpg'); }
  .teaser-bg-2 { background-image: url('./images/thumb2.jpeg'); }
  .teaser-bg-3 { background-image: url('./images/thumb3.jpg'); }
  .teaser-bg-4 { background-image: url('./images/thumb4.jpg'); }
  .teaser-overlay {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.9) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.35) 50%, transparent 100%);
  }
  .teaser-body {
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    padding: 0 2.8rem 4.5rem; max-width: 820px;
  }
  .teaser-num {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .teaser-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem,3.5vw,2.8rem); font-weight: 600; color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }
  .teaser-quote {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem,1.6vw,1.1rem);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72); font-weight: 300; font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--accent); padding-left: 1rem; max-width: 600px;
  }
  .teaser-text {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem,1.4vw,1rem);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-weight: 300; line-height: 2.0; max-width: 660px;
  }
  .teaser-text p + p { margin-top: 0.9rem; }

  /* ─── 타임라인 ─── */
  .timeline-section {
    padding: 6rem 2.8rem;
    max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .timeline-section > h2 {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem,2.8vw,2rem); font-weight: 600; color: var(--black); margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }
  .timeline { position: relative; padding-left: 1.8rem; border-left: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .timeline-item { position: relative; margin-bottom: 3rem; padding-left: 1.6rem; }
  .timeline-item::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute;
    left: -2.25rem; top: 0.45rem;
    width: 8px; height: 8px;
    background: var(--accent); border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .timeline-item.highlight::before {
    width: 12px; height: 12px; left: -2.45rem; top: 0.35rem;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(0,158,47,0.2);
  }
  .timeline-date {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }
  .timeline-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--black); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .timeline-item.highlight .timeline-title { color: var(--accent); }
  .timeline-desc {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif; font-size: 0.88rem;
    line-height: 1.85; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 300;
  }
  .timeline-sub {
    margin-top: 0.6rem; padding-left: 1rem; border-left: 2px solid var(--border);
  }
  .timeline-sub p {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif; font-size: 0.82rem;
    line-height: 1.8; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }
  .timeline-sub p strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }

  /* ─── 기사 카드 ─── */
  .series-section {
    padding: 6rem 2.8rem;
    max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .series-section > .section-label { margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .series-section > h2 {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem,3vw,2.2rem); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 2.8rem; color: var(--black);
  }
  .cards-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
  .card {
    position: relative; aspect-ratio: 16/10; border-radius: 3px;
    overflow: hidden; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; display: block;
  }
  .card-img {
    position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
    background-size: cover; background-position: center; transition: transform 0.55s ease;
  }
  .card:hover .card-img { transform: scale(1.04); }
  .card-overlay {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to top,rgba(0,0,0,0.82) 0%,rgba(0,0,0,0.15) 55%,transparent 100%);
    transition: background 0.4s;
  }
  .card:hover .card-overlay {
    background: linear-gradient(to top,rgba(0,0,0,0.92) 0%,rgba(0,0,0,0.3) 55%,transparent 100%);
  }
  .card-body { position: absolute; bottom:0; left:0; right:0; padding: 1.6rem 1.4rem; }
  .card-num {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .card-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif; font-size: clamp(1.1rem,1.8vw,1.35rem);
    font-weight: 600; color: #fff; line-height: 1.55; margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }
  .card-link-label {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: var(--accent); text-transform: uppercase;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem;
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(5px); transition: opacity 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
  }
  .card:hover .card-link-label { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
  .card-link-label::after { content:'→'; font-size:0.9rem; }
  .img-1 { background-image: url('./images/thumb1.jpg'); }
  .img-2 { background-image: url('./images/thumb2.jpeg'); }
  .img-3 { background-image: url('./images/thumb3.jpg'); }
  .img-4 { background-image: url('./images/thumb4.jpg'); }

  /* ─── 보도 유의사항 ─── */
  .note-section { padding: 4rem 2.8rem; max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .note-box {
    border: 1px solid var(--border); border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    padding: 1.6rem 2rem; background: rgba(0,158,47,0.03);
  }
  .note-label {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }
  .note-text {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif; font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.9; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* ─── 크레딧 ─── */
  .credits-section {
    padding: 5.5rem 2.8rem 7rem;
    background: var(--black); color: var(--off-white);
  }
  .credits-inner { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .credits-section .section-label { color: var(--accent); }
  .credits-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif; font-size: clamp(1.5rem,2.8vw,2rem);
    font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 3.5rem; color: var(--off-white);
  }
  .credits-role-group { margin-bottom: 2.8rem; }
  .credits-role-label {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.78rem; letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-bottom: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }
  .credits-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill,minmax(160px,1fr)); gap: 1rem 2rem; }
  .credit-name {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif; font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--off-white); margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }
  .credit-email { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--accent); letter-spacing: 0.03em; }

  /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
  footer {
    background: var(--black); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    padding: 1.8rem 2.8rem 4.5rem;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  }
  .footer-logo { font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent); }
  .footer-copy { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.62rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.22); letter-spacing: 0.1em; }

  /* ─── MOBILE ─── */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .divider { margin: 0 1.4rem; }
    .hero-content { padding: 0 1.4rem 3.5rem; }
    .hero-title { font-size: clamp(2rem,11vw,3rem); }
    .chart-section,.numbers-section,.lead-section,.timeline-section,.series-section,.note-section { padding-left:1.4rem; padding-right:1.4rem; }
    .numbers-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .cards-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .card { aspect-ratio: 4/3; }
    .teaser-body { padding: 0 1.4rem 3rem; }
    .teaser-item { height: 85vh; }
    .credits-section { padding: 4rem 1.4rem 6rem; }
    .credits-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.7rem; text-align: center; padding-bottom: 5.5rem; }
    .scroll-indicator { display: none; }
    .crisis-bar { padding: 0.9rem 1.2rem; }
    .crisis-text { font-size: 0.82rem; }
    .crisis-icon { display: none; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- 배너 -->
<div class="crisis-bar" id="crisisBar">
  <div class="crisis-icon"></div>
  <p class="crisis-text">
    우울감 등 말하기 어려운 고민이 있거나 주변에 이런 어려움을 겪는 가족·지인이 있을 경우
    <strong>자살예방 상담전화(109)</strong> 또는 자살예방 SNS상담 <strong>'마들랜'</strong>에서
    24시간 전문가의 상담을 받을 수 있습니다.
  </p>
  <button class="crisis-close" id="crisisClose" aria-label="닫기">✕</button>
</div>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-label">세계일보 탐사보도팀</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">자살예방법 제4조,<br>국가의 책무</h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">법의 그물 밖에서 — 제도가 놓친 죽음들</p>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-indicator">
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
    <span>Scroll</span>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- 그래프 -->
<section class="chart-section reveal" id="chart">
  <div class="section-label">— 14년의 기록</div>
  <p class="chart-intro">
    2012년 3월 31일 자살예방법이 시행된 이후,
    <strong>매년 자살자 수는 1만3000명 안팎이다.</strong>
  </p>
  <div class="chart-wrap" style="position:relative;">
    <div class="chart-tooltip" id="chartTooltip"></div>
    <svg class="line-chart" viewBox="0 0 900 320" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" id="lineChartSvg">
      <defs>
        <linearGradient id="areaGrad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
          <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#009e2f" stop-opacity="0.14"/>
          <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#009e2f" stop-opacity="0"/>
        </linearGradient>
      </defs>
      <!-- 그리드 -->
      <line x1="60" y1="20" x2="60" y2="260" stroke="#e8e8e8" stroke-width="1"/>
      <line x1="60" y1="260" x2="880" y2="260" stroke="#e8e8e8" stroke-width="1"/>
      <line x1="60" y1="60"  x2="880" y2="60"  stroke="#f2f2f2" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,4"/>
      <line x1="60" y1="110" x2="880" y2="110" stroke="#f2f2f2" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,4"/>
      <line x1="60" y1="160" x2="880" y2="160" stroke="#f2f2f2" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,4"/>
      <line x1="60" y1="210" x2="880" y2="210" stroke="#f2f2f2" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,4"/>
      <!-- Y축 -->
      <text x="52" y="64"  text-anchor="end" font-family="DM Mono,monospace" font-size="10" fill="#bbb">15,000</text>
